                <trailer/>
                <names>
                    <name>
                        <ln>Stuart</ln>
                        <pf>A. H. H.</pf>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>Report on upcoming meeting to select candidates for state Senate and House
                    of Delegates. Encourages men to participate, take note of the qualifications of
                    the candidates. A.H.H. Stuart will address the group</summary>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
