            <div type="a">
                <column>3</column>
                <head>High Winds</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Gale force winds blew on 3/15, pushing people over and damaging several
                    buildings. The hospital's tin roof was ripped up; the skylight fell in at
                    Rankins Daguerrotype gallery and the gable end of a brick warehouse was blown
                    in.</summary>
            </div>
